    "body": "This transfers the tests from the old coin selection test framework that was based on ignoring fees to the new coin selection framework that tests the coin selection algorithms with realistic feerates and fees.\r\n\r\nThe PR also includes a minor improvement of the test framework to allow the CoinSelectionParams used by the tests to be initialized with other feerates, and adds some feerates around the new minimum feerate to the tested feerates.",
